post.description:
Submit new NZ financing statement based registration template collateral to PPSR register (asynchronous API command).\
Progress can be determined via web hook call-backs or via polling the `/progress` endpoint.
            
Sample request:
```JSON
{
   "customerRequestId" : "acme-12345",
   "securedPartyGroupId" : "51682",
   "clientReference" : "my best template",
   "templateIdentifier" : "mv-og",
   "debtors" : [
     {
       "debtorType" : "organisation",
       "nzbn" : "9429031854290",
       "personJobTitle" : "Developer"
     }
   ]
   "collateralOverrides" : [
       {
           "templateCollateralSequenceNumber" : 1,
           "registrationPlate" : "abc123"
       }
   ]
}
```
Sample Response
```JSON
{
   "resource": {
       "customerRequestId": "acme-12345",
       "ppsrCloudId": "9c7ab5d7-8507-4db6-bca0-8f5b14a2273f"
   },
   "errors": null,
   "hasError": false,
   "warnings": null,
   "hasWarning": false
}
```

Submit new generic NZ financing statement to PPSR register (asynchronous API command).
Progress can be determined via web hook call-backs or via polling the `/progress` endpoint.
            
Sample request:
```JSON
{
   "customerRequestId" : "acme-12345",
   "securedPartyGroupId" : "51682",
   "clientReference" : "my best template",
   "debtors" : [
     {
       "debtorType" : "organisation",
       "nzbn" : "9429031854290",
       "personJobTitle" : "Developer"
     }
   ]
   "collateral" : [
       {
           "collateralType" : "OTH",
           "collateralDescription" : "some item to secure"
       }
   ]
}
```
Sample Response
```JSON
{
   "resource": {
       "customerRequestId": "acme-12345",
       "ppsrCloudId": "9c7ab5d7-8507-4db6-bca0-8f5b14a2273f"
   },
   "errors": null,
   "hasError": false,
   "warnings": null,
   "hasWarning": false
}
```JSON

progresses.description:
Array where each element represents the progress of an individual PPSR search. These individual searches will all have been submitted as a single session or batch of searches,
for example, a collection of grantor searches, serial number searches, registration number searches, etc. Each result will indicate the number of search results for that search,
what % of results have been retrieved and what % of search certificates have been retrieved.

createAccountAdminUser.description:
Optional to indicate whether an account admin user should be created along with the new account. Defaults to false if not specified. \
If true, a user with account admin rights will be created with the following details:
```C#
UserEmail = ContactEmail;
UserFirstName = ContactFirstName;
UserLastName = ContactLastName;
IsAccountAdminUser = true;
IsSsoUser = true;
```
